        <mxCell id="flow-steps" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;font-size:10px;line-height:1.6;&quot;&gt;&#xa;❶ Client creates &lt;b&gt;Workflow&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xa;❷ Client starts &lt;b&gt;Session&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;→ Redis event published&lt;br&gt;&#xa;❸ Agent Service picks up&lt;br&gt;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;→ Calls customer via Twilio&lt;br&gt;&#xa;❹ Deepgram Voice Agent&lt;br&gt;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;→ Guides conversation&lt;br&gt;&#xa;❺ WhatsApp doc request&lt;br&gt;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;→ Customer uploads docs&lt;br&gt;&#xa;❻ Verification Service&lt;br&gt;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;→ OCR + criteria check&lt;br&gt;&#xa;❼ Pass → next doc&lt;br&gt;&#xa;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Fail → re-upload&lt;br&gt;&#xa;❽ All done → &lt;b&gt;COMPLETED&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xa;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontColor=#555555;" vertex="1" parent="1">
